T1  - Efficacy and safety of acupuncture on oligomenorrhea due to polycystic ovary syndrome: An international multicenter, pilot randomized controlled trial.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1097/MD.0000000000028674
A1  - Park, Kyoung Sun
A1  - Gang, Weijuan
A1  - Kim, Pyung-Wha
A1  - Yang, Changsop
