T1  - The impact of irritable bowel syndrome on health-related quality of life in women with polycystic ovary syndrome.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1186/s12955-020-01428-7
A1  - Bazarganipour, Fatemeh
A1  - Taghavi, Seyed-Abdolvahab
A1  - Asemi, Zatollah
A1  - Allan, Helen
A1  - Khashavi, Zahra
A1  - Safarzadeh, Tahereh
A1  - Pourchangiz, Shamsi
