ID  - 30052961
T1  - Recommendations from the international evidence-based guideline for the assessment and management of polycystic ovary syndrome.
T3  - Erratum in: Hum Reprod. 2019 Feb 1;34(2):388 PMID: 30521039 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/30521039]
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1093/humrep/dey256
A1  - Teede, Helena J
